properties.name: id
properties.description: Auto generated 10 characters alphanumeric string

properties.name: name
properties.description: Entry name (Min 1 chars)

properties.name: description
properties.description: Entry description

properties.name: userId
properties.description: The ID of the user who is the owner of this entry

properties.name: creatorId
properties.description: The ID of the user who created this entry

properties.name: tags
properties.description: Entry tags

properties.name: adminTags
properties.description: Entry admin tags can be updated only by administrators

properties.name: categories
properties.description: Comma separated list of full names of categories to which this entry belongs. Only categories that don't have entitlement (privacy context) are listed, to retrieve the full list of categories, use the categoryEntry.list action.

properties.name: categoriesIds
properties.description: Comma separated list of ids of categories to which this entry belongs. Only categories that don't have entitlement (privacy context) are listed, to retrieve the full list of categories, use the categoryEntry.list action.

properties.name: moderationStatus
properties.description: Entry moderation status

properties.name: moderationCount
properties.description: Number of moderation requests waiting for this entry

properties.name: type
properties.description: The type of the entry, this is auto filled by the derived entry object

properties.name: createdAt
properties.description: Entry creation date as Unix timestamp (In seconds)

properties.name: updatedAt
properties.description: Entry update date as Unix timestamp (In seconds)

properties.name: rank
properties.description: The calculated average rank. rank = totalRank / votes

properties.name: totalRank
properties.description: The sum of all rank values submitted to the baseEntry.anonymousRank action

properties.name: votes
properties.description: A count of all requests made to the baseEntry.anonymousRank action

properties.name: partnerData
properties.description: Can be used to store various partner related data as a string

properties.name: downloadUrl
properties.description: Download URL for the entry

properties.name: searchText
properties.description: Indexed search text for full text search

properties.name: licenseType
properties.description: License type used for this entry

properties.name: version
properties.description: Version of the entry data

properties.name: thumbnailUrl
properties.description: Thumbnail URL

properties.name: accessControlId
properties.description: The Access Control ID assigned to this entry (null when not set, send -1 to remove)

properties.name: startDate
properties.description: Entry scheduling start date (null when not set, send -1 to remove)

properties.name: endDate
properties.description: Entry scheduling end date (null when not set, send -1 to remove)

properties.name: referenceId
properties.description: Entry external reference id

properties.name: replacingEntryId
properties.description: ID of temporary entry that will replace this entry when it's approved and ready for replacement

properties.name: replacedEntryId
properties.description: ID of the entry that will be replaced when the replacement approved and this entry is ready

properties.name: replacementStatus
properties.description: Status of the replacement readiness and approval

properties.name: partnerSortValue
properties.description: Can be used to store various partner related data as a numeric value

properties.name: conversionProfileId
properties.description: Override the default ingestion profile

properties.name: redirectEntryId
properties.description: IF not empty, points to an entry ID the should replace this current entry's id.

properties.name: rootEntryId
properties.description: ID of source root entry, used for clipped, skipped and cropped entries that created from another entry

properties.name: parentEntryId
properties.description: ID of source root entry, used for defining entires association

properties.name: operationAttributes
properties.description: clipping, skipping and cropping attributes that used to create this entry

arrayType.description: Base class to all operation attributes types

properties.name: entitledUsersEdit
properties.description: list of user ids that are entitled to edit the entry (no server enforcement) The difference between entitledUsersEdit and entitledUsersPublish is applicative only

properties.name: entitledUsersPublish
properties.description: list of user ids that are entitled to publish the entry (no server enforcement) The difference between entitledUsersEdit and entitledUsersPublish is applicative only

properties.name: capabilities
properties.description: Comma seperated string of the capabilities of the entry. Any capability needed can be added to this list.

properties.name: templateEntryId
properties.description: Template entry id

properties.name: playlistContent
properties.description:
Content of the playlist - 
	 XML if the playlistType is dynamic 
	 text if the playlistType is static 
	 url if the playlistType is mRss

properties.name: idEqual
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only a specific entry (identified by its entryId).

properties.name: idIn
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving few specific entries (string should include comma separated list of entryId strings).

properties.name: nameLike
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It should include only one string to search for in entry names (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: nameMultiLikeOr
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry names, while applying an OR logic to retrieve entries that contain at least one input string (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: nameMultiLikeAnd
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry names, while applying an AND logic to retrieve entries that contain all input strings (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: nameEqual
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving entries with a specific name.

properties.name: partnerIdEqual
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries which were uploaded by/assigned to users of a specific Kaltura Partner (identified by Partner ID).

properties.name: partnerIdIn
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries within Kaltura network which were uploaded by/assigned to users of few Kaltura Partners  (string should include comma separated list of PartnerIDs)

properties.name: userIdEqual
properties.description: This filter parameter should be in use for retrieving only entries, uploaded by/assigned to a specific user (identified by user Id).

properties.name: tagsLike
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It should include only one string to search for in entry tags (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: tagsMultiLikeOr
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry tags, while applying an OR logic to retrieve entries that contain at least one input string (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: tagsMultiLikeAnd
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry tags, while applying an AND logic to retrieve entries that contain all input strings (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: adminTagsLike
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It should include only one string to search for in entry tags set by an ADMIN user (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: adminTagsMultiLikeOr
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry tags, set by an ADMIN user, while applying an OR logic to retrieve entries that contain at least one input string (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: adminTagsMultiLikeAnd
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries. It could include few (comma separated) strings for searching in entry tags, set by an ADMIN user, while applying an AND logic to retrieve entries that contain all input strings (no wildcards, spaces are treated as part of the string).

properties.name: categoriesMatchOr
properties.description: All entries within these categories or their child categories.

properties.name: categoriesIdsMatchOr
properties.description:
All entries of the categories, excluding their child categories.
	 To include entries of the child categories, use categoryAncestorIdIn, or categoriesMatchOr.

properties.name: statusEqual
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries, at a specific {

properties.name: statusNotEqual
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries, not at a specific {

properties.name: statusIn
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries, at few specific {

properties.name: statusNotIn
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving only entries, not at few specific {

properties.name: typeIn
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving entries of few {

properties.name: createdAtGreaterThanOrEqual
properties.description: This filter parameter should be in use for retrieving only entries which were created at Kaltura system after a specific time/date (standard timestamp format).

properties.name: createdAtLessThanOrEqual
properties.description: This filter parameter should be in use for retrieving only entries which were created at Kaltura system before a specific time/date (standard timestamp format).

properties.name: searchTextMatchAnd
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries while search match the input string within all of the following metadata attributes: name, description, tags, adminTags.

properties.name: searchTextMatchOr
properties.description: This filter should be in use for retrieving specific entries while search match the input string within at least one of the following metadata attributes: name, description, tags, adminTags.

properties.name: categoryAncestorIdIn
properties.description: All entries within this categoy or in child categories

properties.name: redirectFromEntryId
properties.description: The id of the original entry

properties.name: totalResults
properties.description: Maximum count of results to be returned in playlist execution

properties.name: playlistType
properties.description: Type of playlist

properties.name: plays
properties.description: Number of plays

properties.name: views
properties.description: Number of views

properties.name: duration
properties.description: The duration in seconds

properties.name: executeUrl
properties.description: The url for this playlist

description:
Update existing playlist
